title: Tech set for Tuesday tussle with Radford at English Field - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech set for Tuesday tussle with Radford at English Field  VT hokiesports.com
description: Having prevailed during its first ACC Coastal Division series of the 2022 season, the Virginia Tech baseball team (12-6) will take a brief step out conference play on Tuesday, March 22, when Tech hosts Radford (6-13) at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
